social_posts.post_text: Stills from the new Cosmic collection by @vestiumny —/ shot in Joshua Tree with a stellar crew ⚡️#vestium #suits #customsuits #stills #joshuatree #ad #luxury #models #hyperbolic
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Cream’ a short film about loneliness, ice cream and the passage of time — link in my story. Music by Mr. Flash
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Matin Lunaire’ a short film about colors and the moon — link in my story. Music by @plaidmusic
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Long Long Summer’ a fashion film about boredom for @paulette — link in my story. Music by @shugi.music
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Dans le bleu du Ciel’ a music video for @loumusiqueofficiel — link in my story — produced by @leftproductions
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Entre Ciel et Mer’ a commercial for @eres with @loancha — link in my story — produced by @jocrantelle
We shot the Cosmic collection from @vestiumny in Joshua Tree with a stellar cast @misssalinas @goddessobiani @justomar4 @cameronmorrelldouglas and my favorite cinematographer @ernestolomeli_dp
Dusk in Joshua Tree —
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Nite Bites’ a music video for Faded Away with @roxane_mesquida & @flashos — link in my story
Gold rush in Joshua Tree —

Throwback Tuesday — ‘One Step’ a short film with @dzubaolya & @joetongofficial — link in my story — hypnotic music by @johntejadaofficial and also my very first collaboration with cinematographer @ernestolomeli_dp ✨

Throwback Tuesday — ‘Pearl Cadillac’ a music video shot in 35mm for @garyclarkjr — link in my story — one of my favorite project made with a pack of amazing people @devinsarno @ernestolomeli_dp and produced by @roger_m._mayer and @leftproductions
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Outro’ a music video for @iforgotmyname_x2 with @mooncube — link in my story — no color correction, no crew, no prep, just the two of us and a couple of hours…
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Renaissance’ a film for Morreale Paris with @loganpolish — link in my story — first of a commercial trilogy produced by @maximerancon
Throwback Tuesday — ‘Meridien’ a film for Morreale Paris with @mvx & @yourotherlover — link in my story — third of a commercial trilogy produced by @maximerancon
